{"id":"5e9c2daf9b6559241525d743","artists":["5e9b68f27a1236eccfeb2014"],"title":"New: Escalier – Stillness","content":"<p>Sometimes a piece of music simply comes at the right time, with the quality or indeed cultural relevance of the piece becoming ultimately meaningless.</p><p> That’s not to say that this new cut of ambient art from<strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Escalier/126016730768965\">Escalier</a></strong> has no artistic merit, for from it, more that its relevance to me is perfectly married to what I need from music at the moment. The piece itself is a simple evolution of sound; it paradoxically blends warm and cold textures, resulting in a piece that embodies the season. It really will make you pause, consider and rebuild.</p>\n<p>Stream the track below.</p>\n<p><object width=\"100%\" height=\"81\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" codebase=\"https://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><param name=\"src\" value=\"https://player.soundcloud.com/player.swf?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F26527800\" /><embed width=\"100%\" height=\"81\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" src=\"https://player.soundcloud.com/player.swf?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F26527800\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" /></object></p>\n","slug":"12139-new-escalier-stillness","category":"music","date":1319724008000,"wpid":12139,"isSticky":false,"featured_image":{"width":165,"height":109,"src":"2011/10/escalier-165x109.jpg","placeholder":"data:image/jpeg;base64, "},"createdAt":1587293615783,"updatedAt":1588403545587,"author":"5e9b68b27a1236eccfeb1d24","old_image":"2011/10/escalier-165x109.jpg","categories":["music","new"]}